text: Htoo Khant Lwin ( player profile at the-afc.com; born 26 October 1998) is a footballer from Burma, and an defender for Yangon United. He was born in Mawlamyine. Yangon United Coach signed Htoo Khant Lwin from Yangon United Youth team for 2019 season.young player at ygnutd.com In March 2019 , Htoo Khant Lwin was chosen for 2020 AFC U-23 Championship qualification squad.
